These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, musical, animation, time-travel, action, crime
6 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, domino, monopoly, scrabble, poker
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person playing scrabble is between the person watching crime movies and the person playing backgammon##2
5. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing billiard##2
6. the person playing backgammon is the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person playing poker is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery | musical | crime | action | time-travel    | animation  |
| Game   | poker | billiard   | monopoly       | scrabble        | backgammon | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
City: paris, liverpool, prague, hamburg, san-francisco, miami
The people use 6 different means of transport: van, ship, airplane, helicopter, boat, taxi
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to paris##2
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person driving the van##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| City   | liverpool | miami | san-francisco | hamburg | prague | paris  |
| Transport           | taxi | boat  | van | ship    | helicopter  | airplane |

