.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: punk, techno, hip-hop, classical, indie, metal
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cycling, cricket, weightlifting, water-polo, badminton, surfing
1. the fan punk is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the fan classical is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the fan indie##1
5. the fan hip-hop is on the far right##1
6. the fan indie is between the fan classical and the person who's sport is cycling##2
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the fan classical##1
9. the fan techno is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Music-Genre         | techno | punk | metal      | indie | classical | hip-hop      |
| Sport   | cricket    | surfing  | cycling | water-polo   | badminton       | weightlifting |

