.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: gospel, house, electronic, soul, blues, rock
The people have 6 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, magic-tricks, writing, collecting, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan soul##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the fan electronic##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the fan house##1
5. the fan gospel is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the fan rock##2
7. the fan house is on the left of the fan rock##1
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Music-Genre        | house    | rock | electronic | gospel | blues | soul   |
| Hobby   | writing | collecting        | gardening  | traveling     | video-games  | magic-tricks |

