.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
City: hannover, new-york, paris, hamburg, london, berlin
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up, lemonade, juice, hot-chocolate
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to london##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
8. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| City   | hannover   | hamburg    | berlin | paris | new-york | london   |
| Beverage         | juice | soy-milk | 7up | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | iced-tea |

