.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, ship, roller, airplane, jet-ski, quad-bike
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: documentary, comedy, sports, superhero, zombie, musical
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person driving the ship##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching musical movies##2
9. the person driving the car is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Transport    | car | quad-bike | jet-ski  | airplane      | roller | ship  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | sports    | superhero | documentary | zombie | musical |

