.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
6 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, lizard, hedgehog, cat, frog
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, aconite, daffodil, poppy, azalea
1. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the hedgehog##2
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who growsazalea##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growspoppy##2
7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growslily##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
9. the person who growsrose is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Pet       | frog | hedgehog | horse | cat | lizard | chinchilla |
| Flower   | aconite | azalea    | poppy  | lily    | daffodil    | rose    |

