3. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsmarigold##2
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who growsaconite##1
5. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the snake##2
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
8. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | bird | snake | rat | guinea-pig | chinchilla |
| Flower   | aconite   | daisy   | daffodil         | marigold    | amaryllis     | rose     |

