 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
