2. the chinese is the person who likes pink##1
3. the person who likes ivory is the colombian##1
4. the person who likes pink is the chinese##1
5. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes grey##2
6. the french is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
7. the person who likes green is on the left of the american##1
8. the person who likes green is between the person who likes mauve and the polish##2
9. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
