.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different games are played: go, scrabble, domino, billiard, snooker, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, august, february, march, october, january
 1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 2. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person playing domino##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 8. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person playing go is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person playing scrabble##2
10. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Game         | mah-jongg   | snooker | domino       | billiard | go    | scrabble |
| Birthday   | august | october  | february | april      | march | january        |

