 1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person who growslily is the owner of the frog##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsaconite and the owner of the cat##2
 5. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the cat and the person who growsdahlia##2
 6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 9. the owner of the cat is the person who growstulip##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Flower           | lily      | aconite | poppy | tulip   | balloon-flower  | dahlia |
| Pet   | frog | lizard  | ferret             | cat | bird | goldfish       |

