.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: train, ship, tram, trike, scooter, boat
There are 6 different nationalities: mexican, australian, russian, polish, egyptian, french
 1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the french is between the egyptian and the person driving the ship##2
 3. the egyptian is between the person driving the boat and the mexican##2
 4. the russian is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 5. the person driving the boat is between the russian and the person driving the tram##2
 6. the person driving the trike is the australian##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the polish is on the right of the australian##1
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Transport   | trike     | train | scooter   | tram     | boat       | ship       |
| Nationality    | australian | polish   | mexican | egyptian | french | russian |

