 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
