.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-16::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: green, coral, aquamarine, ebony, emerald, black
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: february, october, july, december, march, august
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who likes coral##2
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Color   | emerald   | green   | aquamarine        | coral   | black        | ebony   |
| Birthday      | february | march | december | july | august | october |

