.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, car, scooter, skateboard, trike
City: edinburgh, venice, london, nizza, paris, san-francisco
 1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 4. the person traveling to nizza is the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is the person driving the car##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the person traveling to london is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the roller##2
10. the person driving the skateboard is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
